Former wife of APC member, Femi Fani-Kayode (FFK), Precious Chikwendu, has got the internet buzzing with several reactions from people, after she took to social media to applaud her former partner for giving her the opportunity to meet with their children today.
Nigerian beautician, Precious Chikwendu, had earlier on, taken to her official Instagram page to upload a beautiful picture of her rocking a simple outfit, as she revealed that she is going on a play date with her four boys, Joshua, Aragorn, Liam and Ragnar Fani-Kayode.
The former beauty pageant went ahead to appreciate her former husband, FFK, for allowing her to establish contact with their children today.
Here is Precious Chikwendu’s post below;
However, following the revelation of Precious Chikwendu, backed up with her appreciation message to her former partner, her fans and followers took to social media to react, as many congratulated the mother of four on such disclosure.
Others however, went ahead to express shock with regards to her former husband, FFK’s decision to allow Precious Chikwendu see their children today.
